rComments: Dr Grant is definitely one of the best professors. In my opinion, you can't ask to have a professor better than him. He is the type of professor that makes you want to go to lectures. He is clear, funny, and very approachable. He is a fair test maker and marker, but purely memorizing the slides is not good enough, be prepared to apply concepts.
this man gives a crap, speaks with clarity and moderate pace, makes jokes, has good attitude, approachable. what more can you ask for? P.S. he likes his pizza
